## The Skill I Built

In this case, I created an Agent Skill that scaffolds a **.NET solution following Clean Architecture principles**. When invoked, the AI automatically:

1. Creates a new solution  
2. Generates the required projects (e.g., `Domain`, `Application`, `Infrastructure`, `Web`)  
3. Adds project references  
4. Installs necessary NuGet packages  
5. Enforces the expected architecture structure  

Instead of spending **10‚Äì15 minutes** manually setting everything up, the AI creates the entire baseline **in seconds**.

---

## Why This Is Useful

### ‚è± Faster Project Setup
Manual scaffolding is time-consuming. With an Agent Skill, the process becomes nearly instant.  

### üìê Consistent Architecture
Every project starts with the **same conventions and structure**, which is especially helpful for teams working on multiple projects.  

### ü§ñ AI That Executes Workflows
This goes beyond generating code snippets. AI agents can now handle deterministic development tasks, saving you time and reducing errors.  

