## The Bigger Idea

Agent Skills represent a shift in how developers interact with AI. Instead of relying on AI as a passive assistant, we can now **teach it repeatable engineering procedures**.  

Once defined, these skills can serve as building blocks for larger workflows, such as:

- Specification-driven development  
- Automated project scaffolding  
- Environment setup  
- Testing pipelines  

We‚Äôre moving from **AI assistants** to **AI-powered development workflows**‚Äîand the possibilities are exciting.  

